Labels affixed to the device indicate it has an internal :''[[Arcadyan]]'' model of WG7005D12 1-LF-AK. This would seem to be another ''[[Arcadyan]]'' device using :the '''SuperTask!''' RTOS. The default SSID follows the pattern of '''Belkin_G+MIMO_Wireless_XXXXXX''' :where '''XXXXXX''' is the last three octets of the wireless interface MAC :w/ upper case letters.
